Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(620,670)}<Immunity>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 人类种要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到 到底是怎么回事啊 夸下那种海口…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非常抱歉 对不起 我没有预料到舞台是东京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们对这里没辙 我们的主场其实是客场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是万分抱歉我们排不上用场 请自己想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里是主人们的世界吗？
Comment: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你曾经很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非常非常受世界上的女孩子欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你过着被她们追求的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是 在你的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有一位会砰然心跳的思恋之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然而这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面对接连不断的诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的思恋也会动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你能突破众多的诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将爱传达给思恋之人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an7\fs36}注：恶搞生死格斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Living Or Dead系列番外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Love Or Loved 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}～将恋爱的子弹传达给她～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Living Or Dead系列番外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Love Or Loved 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}～将恋爱的子弹传达给她～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs28\pos(240,267)}<Killing・Giant>\N{\fs40}诱导法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗷嗷～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听得见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欢迎来到游戏中的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次就请你们在这架空场所中进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请让我确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里是架空的场所 并不是实际存在的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说凭你们的想象所创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}游戏用的假想空间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是如此 有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别吓我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶 这不让我脑中闪过好几次心灵创伤吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么生气到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}我差点就要割腕自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}别开玩笑了 老头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对这个舞台是有不满吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}超他X的不满！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有什么可悲伤的非得选这种舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是精神攻击还是找碴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最近在东部联合的年轻人中人气很高的SF舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么特别的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为是在游戏中 所以在某种程度是没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怪不得沐浴着日光也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 冷静一点 这里不是东京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是很像而已 这是凭借他们的想象制作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错 这里是在游戏之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs36\an7}注：女神异闻录 命运石之门 秋叶原之旅\N　　从左到右依次 卡蒂・莱科宁 牧濑红莉栖 里中千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女O异闻录 命O石之门 秋O原之旅之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果是在游戏之中的话就没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}游戏之中？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就让我来说明规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先请看脚下的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请各位用那把枪射击靠近过来的NPC
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 要射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}时而射击 时而爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让她们对你神魂颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是Gal☆Gun啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an7\fs36}注：GalGun少女射击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被迷倒的女孩子会将爱的力量托付给各位然后消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从迷恋之枪所射出的是Love Power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是各位的爱情力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这枪的名字叫迷恋之枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真俗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一方面 各位中的某位被伊纲射中后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就会成为伊纲的爱之奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\blur2\an7}画面字：伊纲碳 LOVE——♥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这叫倒戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全世界的女孩子都对自己笑脸相迎 在这之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有思恋之人对你漠然置之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}传达这份爱的力量让她对你神魂颠倒就是这个游戏的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以上 来自说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说从一开始就得甩开女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以为你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说伊纲让四个人迷上自己 目标是后宫结局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们的目标只是伊纲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最后一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们所在的假想空间无法使用魔法 请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样 还需要更详细说明规则吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我们边玩边确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就先来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每射一击迷恋之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就会消耗Love Power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}通过击破NPC 可以恢复Love Power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}这是做什么 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}太令人不快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被NPC接触 Love Power就会减少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Love Power消耗殆尽后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}NPC就会不再靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\move(640,666,640,710,660,1060)}但是 没有了射出迷恋之枪的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就会变成事实上的无法战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 射击同伴会怎么样 老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以恢复Love Power的耗尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 可以救出被伊纲射中变成爱之奴隶的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 会一时变成射击之人的爱之奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊啊 主人!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的妹妹哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在离我这么近的地方竟然存在如此可爱且可人的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真想把至今都没有注意到你的 我的双眼挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 哥不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们是兄妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉尔 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是在主人的书籍里的三角关系和NTR吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就连不拥有恋爱感情的我都有点感兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉尔 一会要调教你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}请原谅我吧 白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}我是按捺不住兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此 在爱之奴隶的状态的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}机能会完全停止以至于不能控制自己吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找到你们了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们又一起放置我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}空 我的王子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\move(640,666,640,710,390,790)}史蒂芙 你理解至今为止的规则了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 规则什么的都没有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算不知道那种东西 我们的爱也是永远的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 理所当然没有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就把这个像这样 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真令人激动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后扳动食指
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦？ 我到底在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是多么美妙的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然打到障碍物会反弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个弹跳性能是关键 白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有虽然是在游戏中 但是体力和现实中没有太大区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尽可能地减少奔跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}两位我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Comment: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}我不会松手的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}我要和你一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}只要有了我就什么都不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}啊 我 watakushi我～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}嗷嗷～
Comment: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总算是游戏正式开始了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样 菲 看得见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米的视野接收得很清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(410,670)}<WereBeast>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对兽人种来说这种魔法真是不能忍受的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 维持这个术式是很困难的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是为了克拉米 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(380,670)}<WereBeast>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兽人种 其身体能力据说能接近物理极限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面对这种不得了的种族你要怎么战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就让我好好见识一下吧 空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话说 伊纲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你最后一次感觉游戏有趣的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然如此吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个才是这个游戏的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 能做到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目标 NPC
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}假定是棉内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}布的厚度最大为1厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十二点方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}距离 20050
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}射入角 93
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}弹速 300m/s
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可允许击中误差 0.5厘米以下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是我做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}开火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}失败了！为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样都好了 这个笨蛋种族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你到底在高兴什么 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}输了的话就会有很多人变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以必须要赢 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是赢了的话 对方会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了 胸罩破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就知道会是手捂胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么可能会感觉到有趣呢 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个脚步声是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是白 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}往这边来了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没打中 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可能 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊纲碳应该正在大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在集合了世界上核心枪手的FPS类游戏中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}创造了无法动摇的记录的并不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而是白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}运用恶魔般的计算能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}掌握敌人的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从这之中导出的行动模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}算进了可能射击的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接近预知未来的提前射击和回避动作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像是射出的子弹在避开一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白的子弹就像追踪着你打过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这太扯了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能逃了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(640,670)}<Flügel>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天翼种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吉普莉尔 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混淆视线的炸弹 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来是无法飞行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}躲不掉 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请让我在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}衣服可以当盾用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}菲 刚才的看见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 用克拉米的眼睛看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白压倒性的射击虽然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 没想到空在远方静静埋伏的射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她竟然在开枪前就察觉到并进行回避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(605,670)}<WereBeast>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是兽人种的第六感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别瞎说了 能做到这个的话就不是第六感了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而是预知未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出千 也就是耍赖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此 无法证明的作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说成是第六感就无从反驳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们果然通晓这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比我们还懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊纲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们在下面的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白累得动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趁现在攻下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用你说 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无论用什么耍小聪明的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们都不可能有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于轮到我们开展防卫战的时候了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜托了白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第一手既然没有决出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从现在开始就要随机应变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}随机应变？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面对熟知游戏的作弊对手用纯粹的比试来对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在这里遇上 你们死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了以前的怨恨和伊纲大人 空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉尔坏坏 大家丢下我去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不会放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把这家伙带来太失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在笑 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才开始这心脏也好烦 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最后感到游戏很有趣是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好开心 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白大人 下一个战术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉尔好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人 果然是太乱来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是白大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:15:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在游戏中我做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白就能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无论何时都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从今以后也会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 相信白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊？哥哥有怀疑过你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就轮到哥了 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白大人为了保护主人而采取的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 我能理解所以别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白不是没得出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那本身就是答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(680,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是『　　』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连白会成为敌人也包含在内的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(590,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}『　　』的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剩下的我要完成我们所约定的能引导我们走向胜利的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如同魔法般的公式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这么回事吧 白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你去当伊纲的对手帮我争取一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样虽说是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算把她打倒也没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36\blur2}注：出自Fate/Stay night英灵卫宫士郎的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是这个意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还是先吐槽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这常被看作是死亡Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么我就普通地打倒她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}省得我去找人的工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跑去哪里了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你好啊 小狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有种既视感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我之前挑战东部联合然后失败时的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难不成是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然主人叫我争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竭尽一切作弊手段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}直到气消为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请再次给我添上失败的羞耻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这不是场所的差异就能解决的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要我怎么办啊 白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就这样逃到屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 这点也会被预料到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管哪条路都会马上被追上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 不觉得有点怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白为什么不跑着追上来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果用跑着的话 干掉我的时机要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尽可能地减少奔跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说起来这么说的不是我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果会错了意就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了白 哥差不多到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有这么对待家里蹲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事到如今哥是不可能在这里出错的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果有你没有想到的事的话 那就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没有想要回避 没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥也最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊纲 就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是让我费了好大的工夫啊 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你保存体力不去奔跑就是为了这个吧 白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可能 刚被空打到之后应该还不能立刻自由行动才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}内裤没有了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道说！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的只瞄准内裤开枪的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于注意到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白从一开始就从未变成过你们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打中的是衣服 然后伪装中弹 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被算计了 但不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:22:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最后一次觉得玩游戏很有趣是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有趣 desu
Comment: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36\blur2}注：出自最终幻想4
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(830,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还差一把劲了 把力量给『　　』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\blur2\pos(1057,532)}<Rule‧Number‧10>\N{\fs40}收束法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.82,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,ベイビーベイベー  LOVE ME DO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.68,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,愛の囁くよりも速く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:59.57,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,ぎゅっとその引き金を引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.79,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,ベイビーベイベー　DYNAMITE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.50,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,理性ごと吹っ飛ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:11.10,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,あなた以外もう何もいらないくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.46,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,愛の強さ教えて欲しいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:16.90,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,できるでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.48,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,解き放て弾けるパッション
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:25.26,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,ほらめっちゃくちゃメロメロにして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:26.43,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,愛はドッキュン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:27.88,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,恋はズッキュン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:29.98,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,らぶパワー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.33,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,このハートど真ん中命中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:36.28,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,いやよ…だけど　ねぇもう１回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.54,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,愛はド級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:38.83,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,恋は直球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.91,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,らぶモーション
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.36,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,カラダ中痺れちゃう want you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.65,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,強く撃ち抜いてくださいダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.57,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,お願い☆すにゃいぱー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.82,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,宝贝宝贝 爱我吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.68,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,比爱之细语还要快速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:59.57,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,紧紧地扣动你的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.79,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,宝贝宝贝 炸裂开!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.50,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,连同理性一起吹飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:11.10,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,除你以外我再无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.46,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,想要让你告诉给我爱的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:16.90,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,能做到的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.48,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,喷射而出炸裂开来的激情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:25.26,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,来吧 把我迷得神魂颠倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:26.43,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,爱情是心动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:27.88,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,恋爱是心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:29.98,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,爱的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.33,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,命中我心脏的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:36.28,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,不要哟…但是 呐再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.54,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,爱情是顶级
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:38.83,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,恋爱是直球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.91,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,爱的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.36,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,身体兴奋得想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.65,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,亲爱的请用力射穿我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.57,OPCHS,,0,0,0,,拜托了☆射手喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:45.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}誰にも言えない孤独を抱えたまま一人で泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}誰にも上手に笑えない僕ら二人出会って笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}真夜中すぎに　想像の奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}どうしようもない気持ちをただ押しやって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:14.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}サヨナラ　僕らはきっと生まれ変われるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}悲しみに手を振るんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:25.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}そしていつか空っぽのままの心に灯りをともすように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:32.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}とぎれとぎれの　言葉を探して繋ぎ止めた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:38.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}それでもたった二人の世界は続いてくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:46.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}空に祈るように　どうか永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:45.70,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}将无法对别人说出口的孤独藏于心中 一个人哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.66,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}无法对别人好好笑出来的我们 相遇了欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.00,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}在午夜过后之时 在想象深处之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.03,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}只是将无可奈何的心情抛在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:14.90,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}再见了 因为我们一定能够重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.98,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}对悲伤挥挥手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:25.79,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}然后曾经空荡荡的心灵就会像点燃了明灯一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:32.18,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}寻找断断续续的话语 将它们系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:38.05,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}尽管如此两人的世界还是会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:46.76,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}像天空祈祷 请一定要相伴永远
